{"tid":1943133,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"1:1 Minecraft 世界地圖計劃 有無香港建築師/伺服器可以幫手起返香港","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:35:14.000Z","uid":90306,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"270d9ec9eddcba2cd451a3e45eb653cf9f5a7352","tid":1943133,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"早幾日出咗個 mod 係用全世界公開嘅地形資料，去generate <span style=\"color: orange;\">1:1 嘅世界地形</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8_bW3ab8YAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8_bW3ab8YAk&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4ZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=c2d68586\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8_bW3ab8YAk</a><br />\n<br />\n然後就有一班人想起返全個地球所有建築物出嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/69ashjz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F69ashjz&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4ZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=df18db45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/69ashjz</a><br />\n<br />\n現時個Discord已經有 8000 幾人，但我好似未見到有香港人，小弟只係個普通玩家用屋企電腦搭server圍內玩，但好想幫手起 (利申都識用world edit去起吓嘢)。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔知有無識搭server / 有 server 嘅 minecraft 友可以建立一個香港server去成就呢件事?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ba8f79361d7bfda744dfbb9dcf09e7436645b0e","tid":1943133,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8ee201a5b06735f467aa6b9ede23c998d9c766ea","tid":1943133,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"冇玩<br />\n不過推"},{"pid":"27837e7cab1e3ec9372ba33814e5bbdde3518a37","tid":1943133,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f849c819691af16e81fc9b50f6f234af4b482094","tid":1943133,"u